name: LRUMap_getTest
description: Unit tests for the get method of LRUMap, focusing on different scenarios including updating to MRU, not updating to MRU, handling non-existing keys, null keys, and full maps.

test_cases.name: testGetExistingKeyWithUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with an existing key and updates to MRU.

test_cases.name: testGetExistingKeyWithoutUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with an existing key without updating to MRU.

test_cases.name: testGetNonExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a non-existing key.

test_cases.name: testGetNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a null key.

test_cases.name: testGetWithFullMap
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a full map and updates to MRU.

test_cases.name: testGetWithFullMapWithoutUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with a full map without updating to MRU.

test_cases.name: testGetWithEmptyMap
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with an empty map.

test_cases.name: testGetWithMultipleGets
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with multiple gets and updates to MRU.

test_cases.name: testGetWithMultipleGetsWithoutUpdateToMRU
test_cases.description: Tests the get method with multiple gets without updating to MRU.
